data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! This beautiful home will easily qualify for USDA, VA, FHA and other loan programs. Polk county has a phenomenal down payment assistance program for those who qualify.   Allow me to introduce you to 3339 Imperial Manor Way in Mulberry, a serene escape nestled between the two bustling cities of Tampa and Orlando. This home is solidly built, immaculately clean and is in a lovely community that provides a blend of tranquility and accessibility. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home offers ample space for comfortable living. The open-concept design creates an inviting and airy atmosphere, perfect for family gatherings.The well-appointed kitchen features newer appliances and plenty of counter and cabinet space. Your new owners retreat is complete with an en-suite bathroom, providing a private oasis after a long day. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your backyard with plenty of room for the kids and pets to play, as well as grilling, gardening, or simply relaxing. There's definitely ample space for a pool!  This concrete block home features brand new impact resistant and energy efficient windows with a warranty that transfers to the buyer, new gutters, new waterproof luxury vinyl flooring, a new disposal in the kitchen, a new hot water heater, a new shed for additional storage and the roof and HVAC are less than 3 years old.  Buyers should verify all dimensions as they are approximate.
